    excerpt: "Get accurate 2025 renovation costs for Singapore HDB flats and condos. Detailed breakdowns by room, material grade, and flat type to help you budget right.",
    category: "Budget Guides",
    tags: ["renovation cost", "budget", "Singapore", "2025", "pricing", "HDB", "condo"],
    publishDate: "Jan 2025",
    readTime: 11,
