    excerpt: "Minimalist design in Singapore goes beyond white walls and empty shelves. Learn how to create a truly minimal home that is warm, functional, and uniquely yours.",
    category: "Design Trends",
    tags: ["minimalist", "interior design", "Singapore", "HDB", "less is more", "clean lines"],
