    title: "How to Interview an Interior Designer in Singapore: 15 Questions to Ask",
    excerpt: "Before hiring an interior designer in Singapore, ask these 15 critical questions. They reveal competence, reliability, and whether the designer is truly the right fit for your project.",
    category: "House Hacks",
